@startuml
' Embedded standalone style block (replicated per file; standalone)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 3
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

autonumber "<b>"

actor "Administrador\n(rol admin)" as Admin
actor "Personal Logistico\n(rol staff, lectura)" as Staff
boundary "Angular Admin\n(products / Apollo)" as Boundary
control "Catalog resolvers\n(mutations.go)" as Resolvers
control "CatalogService\n(catalog_service.go)" as Service
entity "Product / ProductVariant\n(catalog.go)" as Entity
database "NeonDB\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB
control "Subsistema Documental\n(MS3 documentos)" as MS3

== Lectura del catalogo (Personal Logistico / Administrador) ==
Staff -> Boundary : Abrir listado de productos
Boundary -> Resolvers : query products (POST /graphql)
Resolvers -> Resolvers : requireAuth\n(admin / staff / customer)
Resolvers -> Entity : Leer Product / ProductVariant
Entity -> DB : SELECT products, product_variants
DB --> Entity : filas de catalogo
Entity --> Resolvers : Product / Variant
Resolvers --> Boundary : lista de productos
Boundary --> Staff : Mostrar catalogo (solo lectura)

== Mantenimiento del catalogo (Administrador) ==
Admin -> Boundary : Crear / actualizar / activar / desactivar producto
Boundary -> Resolvers : mutation createProduct / updateProduct /\ncreateVariant / activateProduct / deactivateProduct

alt rol no admin (requireAdmin falla)
  Resolvers --> Boundary : error no autorizado
  Boundary --> Admin : Mostrar error de permisos
else rol admin autorizado
  opt reemplazo de imagen
    Boundary -> Resolvers : mutation replaceProductImage(ID, newImageDocumentID)
    Resolvers -> MS3 : Asociar document id (imagen en S3 privado)
    MS3 --> Resolvers : document id confirmado
  end

  Resolvers -> Service : CreateProduct / CreateVariant (input validado)
  Service -> Entity : Construir / modificar Product / Variant
  Entity -> DB : INSERT / UPDATE products, product_variants

  alt escritura exitosa
    DB --> Entity : ok (filas afectadas)
    Entity --> Service : Product / Variant persistido
    Service --> Resolvers : Product / Variant
    Resolvers --> Boundary : Product / Variant actualizado
    Boundary --> Admin : Refrescar listado de catalogo
  else error de persistencia
    DB --> Entity : error
    Entity --> Service : error
    Service --> Resolvers : error
    Resolvers --> Boundary : error de operacion
    Boundary --> Admin : Mostrar error al usuario
  end
end
@enduml
